冇可能行得郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以<br />\n只要個speed係constant就得<br />\n同埋唔係好快咁由0加速到「 接近光速」<br />\n因為 Fnet=ma<br />\n只要個speed係constant(a=0)<br />\n即係地板畀你嘅force係等於零<br />\n所以你一定行到<br />\n呢個同你平時搭地鐵嘅原理一樣<br />\n只會喺埋站 的時候你先會企唔穩<br />\n但係反而係最高速嘅行車時間嗰陣<br />\n你唔會平衡唔到自己嘅原理一樣<br />\n有講錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4298e72259d402517fb684bb69336247c132f2e3","tid":464319,"uid":15954,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"v=(v1+v2)/(1+v1v2/c^2)"},{"pid":"a011812192d620a30a181518cff68230a7e5008c","tid":464319,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"行得到，架車 相對於外界既速度 同 相對於你既速度 係無關係的"},{"pid":"ace51065207ad70e712d1707f30e14b67b077cef","tid":464319,"uid":121130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行得到，架車 相對於外界既速度 同 相對於你既速度 係無關係的</blockquote><br />\n出面既人見你無行過<br />\n你行路既過程超出時間所能表達<br />\n你既問題可以視為<br />\n在未來是否可以由車頭行到車尾<br />\n答案係no 因為未來唔合適形容你既狀態<br />\n應該係咁"},{"pid":"d5da3bc811241fc60353653cb86c3f9446e305aa","tid":464319,"uid":121130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"sor睇錯左<br />\n我睇左光速<br />\n上面講緊光速既情況"},{"pid":"e7ae26d07e505bfc592e52b4f089478317bc77c5","tid":464319,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"接唔接近光速唔重要<br />\n重要嘅係你相對㗎火車個速度係0<br />\n以我理解就應該行得郁"},{"pid":"f174c75d961c8b89d209bc9d04fa85da5f1db620","tid":464319,"uid":134431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"反問你<br />\n飛機上你行唔行到丫？ <br />\n0.73Mach"},{"pid":"9ef03f34fb007355873385164f269c18189bb83c","tid":464319,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反問你<br />\n飛機上你行唔行到丫？ <br />\n0.73Mach</blockquote><br />\n但係接近光速喎架火車<br />\n係上面行路我嘅速度有冇可能超越光速<br />\n如果有唔會出啲時間勃論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479a740b0ea62d5a11271a3235b4b8a182f7b3fc","tid":464319,"uid":12757,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:23:46.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾中學 出埋算式計 真係笑撚死人<br />\n柒撚到核爆<br />\n<br />\n光速同物體係相對都唔撚識  仲學人拋書包 廢撚到"},{"pid":"62550db966639999953e9f4044b408a3c35875eb","tid":464319,"uid":12757,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反問你<br />\n飛機上你行唔行到丫？ <br />\n0.73Mach</blockquote><br />\n但係接近光速喎架火車<br />\n係上面行路我嘅速度有冇可能超越光速<br />\n如果有唔會出啲時間勃論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 話鳩知你架車係咪光速啦   睇下你同咩野去比架姐<br />\n明就明 唔明你就收皮  因爲你仲停留緊係中學雞階段"},{"pid":"4d678958823cc58eaa96002b0a0bf6fbca72666c","tid":464319,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"你個觀點來講 <br />\n會同平時一樣<br />\n<br />\n其他人個觀點<br />\n答巴打答"},{"pid":"871794d2718b5b8f0a814d50df4d93e2638af929","tid":464319,"uid":32645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>v=(v1+v2)/(1+v1v2/c^2)</blockquote><br />\n正解冇人理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登兒家係咪冇人讀到大學/AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202699e10091b843a352ba9aa9d3b143ddb6a54c","tid":464319,"uid":59136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>v=(v1+v2)/(1+v1v2/c^2)</blockquote><br />\n正解？係唔係漏左個開方？<br />\n（求解）（利申冇讀過）"},{"pid":"604ad6dc2f2d496e592e41fd66385490abd2be3c","tid":464319,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班垃圾中學 出埋算式計 真係笑撚死人<br />\n柒撚到核爆<br />\n<br />\n光速同物體係相對都唔撚識  仲學人拋書包 廢撚到</blockquote><br />\n光速邊係相對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d5019636a8f00dfc3fb64079cf2e217e7ddb96","tid":464319,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"要問一問光速蒙面俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce68f9cd01b9d6a8847c5533568fa7e5a50083e","tid":464319,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"如果喺架接近光速嘅火車屌閪呢"},{"pid":"a0c492010c5151d4edf3e3381b1666ed5e392854","tid":464319,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:39:35.000Z","msg":"冇嘢會發生<br />\n知唔知咩叫相對性原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 唔同其他參考系比較 你唔會知道你自己本身有無運動<br />\n2. 所有物理定律都有相對性<br />\n當然前提係架車係穩定加速至接近光速 而你又承受得到<br />\n亦都唔會突然加減速或者轉彎"},{"pid":"3667fb9d87d35615b477689c783710928861f9bd","tid":464319,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個觀點來講 <br />\n會同平時一樣<br />\n<br />\n其他人個觀點<br />\n答巴打答</blockquote><br />\n對其他觀察者嚟講<br />\n你其實跑得好慢好慢<br />\n假設火車上面有一個光時鐘裝置<br />\n光源同一塊鏡上下垂直 兩者距離1.5萬公里<br />\n換言之 一個來回三萬公里即係光行一秒嘅速度<br />\n接收器收到信號就等於一秒<br />\n光+接收器<br />\n<br />\n鏡<br />\n其他觀察者 望個鐘 因為個火車一路行緊<br />\n會係咁樣:<br />\n光            接收器<br />\n<br />\nxxxx鏡<br />\n所以光行進嘅距離 超過三萬公里<br />\n由於光速不變 於是 一個循環要嘅時間就會長咗<br />\n所以火車上面一秒長咗 時間慢咗<br />\n亦基於相對性原理 所以其他物體嘅行為都會一樣慢咗<br />\n如果非常接近光速 你嘅動作應該係慢到爆<br />\n所以唔存在你跑得快過光速呢樣嘢"},{"pid":"6e4d3bdf0f5b83e86cf49888a17ac555344186d7","tid":464319,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"順帶一提 運動中嘅物體<br />\n佢嘅時間會變慢<br />\n長度會縮短<br />\n質量會增加<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7bc7f4d69a071da1881a0665a971e31f46c454","tid":464319,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反問你<br />\n飛機上你行唔行到丫？ <br />\n0.73Mach</blockquote><br />\n但係接近光速喎架火車<br />\n係上面行路我嘅速度有冇可能超越光速<br />\n如果有唔會出啲時間勃論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係悖論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實呢個問題問得幾好<br />\n可以google下twins paradox<br />\n都幾異曲同工 但係複雜好多<br />\n因為當中牽涉咗lorentz transformation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6021fce33b700278428ccf7c1b14ae70d981dc6b","tid":464319,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成班垃圾中學 出埋算式計 真係笑撚死人<br />\n柒撚到核爆<br />\n<br />\n光速同物體係相對都唔撚識  仲學人拋書包 廢撚到</blockquote><br />\n光速邊係相對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒頭 深潛啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}